{"tid":193124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【鬼門關口】火化前一刻突然呼吸 「已死」早產嬰及時翻生","createTime":"2017-04-09T05:43:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T13:57:27.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f7856d536c75c7d81a6b17367c79959889f52ff1","tid":193124,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T05:43:41.000Z","msg":"2017年04月09日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170408/large/1491644904_331c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170408%2Flarge%2F1491644904_331c.jpg&h=0c5ca7d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印度拉賈斯坦邦（Rajasthan）一名早產嬰可謂「險過剃頭」。有護士在未徵詢醫生意見前，自行判斷一名早產女嬰已死亡，更建議家人當天火化死嬰，就在火化前「數秒」女嬰突然恢復心跳和呼吸，逃過被火化的厄運。<br />\n<br />\n只孕育24周就出世的早產嬰，僅重350克，由於她出生後一動也不動，似乎沒有呼吸及心跳，《印度時報》報道，一名護士在沒有問過醫生的情況下，就直接指女嬰已死。<br />\n親人指，正準備火化女嬰時發現不妥，「當我們拿開她（女嬰）的毛巾，她正在呼吸。於是我們帶她回醫院，院方安排她到深切治療部治理。」有關方面已就事件展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170409/56537966\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170409%2F56537966&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqF5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=478f7078\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170409%2F56537966&h=a633dfb0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170409/56537966</a>"},{"pid":"eb4cbd1fa58569624d17d565157de56340c5105b","tid":193124,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T05:45:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e840dc45597f0952a9a8ded3f8d237b81894648","tid":193124,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T05:46:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78430a0acfb7ec17d725542b3a61efe6593785ff","tid":193124,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T05:51:37.000Z","msg":"點解咁傻，好地地燒咗就唔會比人姦"},{"pid":"85b81b424f30cf9135cbfa6c28f341054d03e5fc","tid":193124,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:34:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a3a17862db486a4f9f14d0f2101bbe7d3dcf14","tid":193124,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:56:13.000Z","msg":"唉，個天真係想玩死佢<br />\n一生一定要受好多苦，死左好過"},{"pid":"c4fd399c63fbee21b95432c20b8c09b7521e1ce8","tid":193124,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:57:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"939d55e6c133c3628552d9cea194c7cc608e6ddb","tid":193124,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:57:27.000Z","msg":"bb都開外掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}